# OpenSpec workflow (EVI)

Before coding a feature:

1. `openspec list` — confirm **one** active change.
2. `openspec instructions apply --change <name> --json` — read only `contextFiles`.
3. Implement the **next unchecked** task; respect `Files:` and `Verify:` in `tasks.md`.

Do **not** read `personal-ai-agent-server.md`, full `Progress.md`, or plan files unless the user asks.

After each task: run `Verify:` command, then mark `- [x]` in `tasks.md`.

When all tasks done: `openspec validate <change>` then `/opsx:archive`.

See [openspec/AGENTS.md](../../openspec/AGENTS.md).
